8.16.21  3:36 pm   What do you think about this?: Opportunities usually pop up once or twice, but never enough times to confirm that you SHOULD do it. You either do it or you don't. Very rarely does an opportunity pop up where it tells you in the moment, "Hey, do me! Take me! Take this opportunity!". That is decided by you in the moment, like a test or a game. Only when you realize that you didn't take it and you regret not doing it do you realize it was speaking to you to take the opportunity all along.
